Farming Assistant Web Services

login & register page for farmers
login & register page for dealers
login for admin
complaints page write only by farmers add read only by dealers and read and edit by admin
advertisement page for dealers
get notification to farmers
Ordering of seeds from dealers by farmers
farmers wishlist,cartlist
notifiaction(advertisement,exhibition,weather report,latest product price,upcoming agree training)
dealer can respond to their complaints receivrd by farmers
admin can update where the upcoming agricultural exhibition is.



